high_descs: pick up the pink soap bar from the toilet tank
walk right to face the sink
wash the soap in the sink, pick up the soap from the sink
step slightly to the right of the sink to face the counter top
put the soap on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: put a washed bar of soap on a bathroom counter

high_descs: Walk to the toilet on your left.
Grab a soap bar from the toilet.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the soap bar in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the soap bar on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Wash a soap bar and put it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the clean bar of soap on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the counter.
